WEBVTT

00:11:58.739 --> 00:12:02.518
they were literally getting an artifact
from the utopian future,

00:12:02.542 --> 00:12:05.083
sort of a blueprint
for an attainably utopian future

00:12:05.107 --> 00:12:08.505
brought about by this very important idea
of popular pressure.

00:12:09.931 --> 00:12:11.956
And our hoax worked perfectly.

00:12:11.980 --> 00:12:14.334
We suspended people
in this strange mental space,

00:12:14.358 --> 00:12:17.094
because while the stories
in the paper couldn't be real,

00:12:17.118 --> 00:12:20.141
it just felt so perfectly,
impeccably real.

00:12:20.165 --> 00:12:22.184
Here's a video showing --

00:12:22.208 --> 00:12:24.406
(Laughter)

00:12:24.430 --> 00:12:26.230
yes, we did that! --

00:12:26.254 --> 00:12:28.685
showing the first few seconds
of conflicted belief,

00:12:28.709 --> 00:12:30.856
where people could feel
for a moment what --